Return & Refund Policy

If you receive a damaged or incorrect product, you may request a return within 24 hours of delivery. Please contact us on WhatsApp with your order details and product photos.

Conditions for Return

  • Item must be unused and in original condition
  • Return request must be made within 24 hours
  • Unboxing video required for damaged product claims

Non-Returnable Items

  • Artificial jewellery cannot be returned due to hygiene reasons
  • Returns accepted only for damaged or incorrect items

Refund / Replacement

Replacement will be provided after verification. If unavailable, refund will be issued within 3-5 working days.
